data.description: Spacious 1.5 story on a cul-de-sac, backs to trees with fully finished walk out basement in the Heart of Wentzville! This 5 bedroom, 3.5 bath home has appealing features like woodburning fireplace in the Great Room with wall of windows overlooking trees, Kitchen with 42" cabinets, backsplash, and center island with overhang. Master Bedroom on the main level features a coffered ceiling with ceiling fan, bay windows, walk in closet and luxury bath.  Separate Dining Room/Office, oversized Main Floor Laundry and 1/2 bath complete the main level.  Upstairs is massive Bonus Room and 3 other spacious bedrooms.  The lower level offers a 5th Bedroom, Recreation Room, 4th bathroom and a beautiful bar for entertaining!  3 car garage, neighborhood pool, maintenance-free deck, large patio, newer roof and HVAC are just a few of the other features. Minutes away from Interstates, shopping, dining and Recreation Center.  Home is to be sold "as is", Sellers recognize the home needs paint and carpet.
